 }}</ref>

IEEE 802.3的“400 Gb/s以太网研究组”于2013年3月开始制定400 Gbit/s标准。<ref>{{Cite web |title= 400 Gb/s Ethernet Study Group |url= http://www.ieee802.org/3/400GSG/ |work= Group web site |publisher= IEEE 802.3 |accessdate= May 23, 2013 |archive-date= 2013-04-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130407004836/http://www.ieee802.org/3/400GSG/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>研究组成果于2014年3月27日公布并被批准。随后，IEEE 802.3bs工作组<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ieee802.org/3/bs/ |title=IEEE 802.3bs Task Force |accessdate=2018-01-06 |archive-date=2020-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603072603/http://www.ieee802.org/3/bs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>开始努力为数种链路距离提供物理层规范。<ref name="obj">{{Cite web |title=Objectives |publisher=IEEE 802.3bs Task Force |date=Mar 2014 |url=http://www.ieee802.org/3/bs/Objectives_14_0320.pdf |accessdate=2015-03-01 |archive-date=2014-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217233130/http://www.ieee802.org/3/bs/Objectives_14_0320.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

IEEE P802.3bs标准于2017年12月6日获得批准<ref name="approval"/>并在线发布。<ref>{{Cite web |title=P802.3bs - IEEE Standard for Ethernet Amendment: Media Access Control Parameters, Physical Layers and Management Parameters for 200 Gb/s and 400 Gb/s Operation |publisher=IEEE 802.3bs Task Force |url=http://standards.ieee.org/findstds/standard/802.3bs-2017.html |accessdate=2017-12-14 |archive-date=2018-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201014028/http://standards.ieee.org/findstds/standard/802.3bs-2017.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

